<h1>WDJSP Source Code</h1>
<p>
This archive contains the Java classes and sample JSP pages from
the book <i>Web Development with JavaServer Pages</i> by 
<a href="mailto:dkf@taglib.com">Duane Fields</a>
and
<a href="mailto:mak@taglib.com">Mark Kolb</a>
(Manning Publications, April 2000, ISBN 1884777996).
Information regarding updates and new versions of this source code
distribution can be found on-line at
<a href="http://www.taglib.com/">www.taglib.com</a>.
</p>

